reviewText: Gene, Roy, Dale, et al are a part of my youth. I will watch them at every opportunity! My age ? 79!
the Quality was real good and I am Very pleased with the packaging and the case it came in real  OK

Gene Autry always wore a white hat, rode a palomino named Champion, was the best with his guns and fists and could sing better than any cowboy in the movies.  Any fan of old western movies would have to enjoy this.

As yet I haven't taken the time to view this dvd.  There are 4 movies on the dvd.  I recognize the movie titles, and as I recall, they are good.  Mr. Autry was always one of my very favorite western actors.  An Authentic American Hero from World War II.
The volume 2 was delivered at the same time as Volume 1, and in good condition.  I've ordered from other vendors (not Amazon Marketplace vendors) The dvd Cases were cracked or otherwise damaged.  Some of the video's just didn't play well.  I have never had a case or a dvd that was delivered from Amazon or the Market Place Vendors that were delivered in any condition but AWESOME!!  Thanks Amazon for the service.
This DVD has 4 movies with Gene Autry and they were great to watch and I will enjoy watching them again and again. Glad that I bought them for myself.
These DVDs are for anyone who remembers Gene Autry and loves the old westerns where the good guys always win.  This is a collection I will always keep and watch often.
These movies have been restored nicely.  They're over 80 years old but don't crackle and pop.
I am very satisfied with this purchase.
Another DVD of Gene Autry. Thanks! I collect them.
GREAT WESTERNS AND WAITING MAKES A BETTER PRICE.
Watching them catch the bad guys and clean up towns of Gangsters remind me of the same things that are still with us today.
